<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_592_r1l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als vns ewr gnade <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von Hanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_592_r1l4">Rorvvolffs wegen . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Vnd alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_592_r1l5">vvenn Er <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd dem palmtag ſchıerſt hercʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_592_r1l6">vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wil . So ſol Er durch ewrn willen / cʒu vnd von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_592_r1l7">vns für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . Vnd bey vns für <expan>allermenkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_592_r1l8">drey tag geleyte <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Alſdan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllen vvir ſein rede hören </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_592_r1l9"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden lieb vnd dinſt beweiſen möhten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_592_r1l10">des wern vvir wıllig vnd teten eʒ <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> in <expan>vıg<ex>ilia</ex></expan> </ab>
